# Copy to ".env.local" (or set in Vercel). Restart Vite after changes.
#
# --- WebSocket relay (required) ---
# Vite bakes `VITE_*` at **build** time. Vercel: Project → Settings → Environment Variables → Production → Redeploy.
#
# Your Render Web Service URL, WebSocket scheme. No path; room is added as `?room=CODE`.
# Example after you deploy `server/` to Render:
# VITE_RELAY_URL=wss://contact-relay-xxxx.onrender.com
#
# HTTPS pages (Vercel, local Vite + basicSsl) must use **wss://**. `ws://` is blocked as mixed content.
# Local relay without TLS: either test the static build over HTTP only, or use the hosted `wss://` URL from Render.
#
# Vite may print https://198.18.0.1:5173/ — that is NOT your LAN (often VPN/Clash fake-ip). Use https://192.168.x.x on the phone.
